Package: gguidance
Title: Extended guide options for 'ggplot2'
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Teun",
           family = "van den Brand",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "tahvdbrand@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9335-7468"))
Description: A 'ggplot2' extension that focusses on expanding the plotter's 
    arsenal of guides, such as axes, legends and colour bars. It brings
    various improvements to existing guides by re-implementation, as well as
    adding novel guides.
